<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>42</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lungthim kipak chengte,
 Hukdampa min ngaite;
 Na theihtawp uh suoh un,
 A min chawian dingin;
 Gamtin, muntin a mi hilh un, (2)
 A hehpih lei na bat u chuh.

[V2]
 2. A Lallukhuk nusie'n,
 Lalpuon lopi kawihtha'n;
 Hehpih tha'n A hung suk,
 Kap leh liem in A thii;
 A thawk natzie gen theih ei puoi, (2)
 Thihna apat ei hukdam di'n.

[V3]
 3. Mithite umna mun,
 Than thim apat A tho;
 Tichun A galte chu,
 Lopi takin A zo;
 Galhat van ah A kal to ta'i, (2)
 Hukdampa'n vanah vai A hawm.

[V4]
 4. Kin takin hung intin,
 Chawmkhat le chawllo in;
 I thagau uh pui ding,
 Ni tawplo gam achun;
 Ziechun A hehpih mel mu'i tiu, (2)
 A angsung ah umzing ta'i tiu.</lyrics>
<title>COME, EVERY JOYFUL HEART!</title>
</song>